## Code Availability

This repository has been created to support the reproducibility of the manuscript.  
Since the manuscript is currently under review, the full implementation has not been publicly released at this stage.

Upon acceptance or publication, we will release:
- the implementation of MAE-TPFNet;
- the customized modules, including STPA, ST-CSA, and GAF-Head;
- training and testing configuration files;
- preprocessing and evaluation scripts;
- instructions for reproducing the reported experiments.

The repository will be continuously updated.
